The paper deals with data mining algorithms and proposes a distributed approach for building a global SVM model. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of handling large data sets, which could fall under the sub-categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of SVM for classification, which could fall under the sub-category of Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
